<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE en-export SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/evernote-export2.dtd"><en-export export-date="20130826T134738Z" application="Evernote/Windows" version="4.x"><note><title>My Ideas #25</title><content><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note style="background: #cccccc;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',  Helvetica, Arial, 'Liberation Sans', FreeSans, sans-serif;color: #585957;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.3;"><?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>            <!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd">            <en-note style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space;">            #TweetDeckhacks: (15). Combine all tweets into a single column and filter-out repeated tweets that are too similar to those already seen.3 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>@TweetDeckhacks: (14). Automatically update to the latest TweetDeck whenever a new version is available.3 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>@TweetDeckhacks: (13). Automatically translate tweets that are not in preferred language using latest Google AI API.8 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>@TweetDeckhacks: (12). Watch for and collect tweets I said I was interested in based on those tweets I have clicked, for later.9 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (11). Don't show me tweets that are too similar to those I have already seen.13 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (10). Allow me to edit my last tweet with a single keystroke.21 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (9). Automatically follow those who follow me and direct message each with a nice "hello and thanks".27 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (8). Allow tweets to span 140 char limits automatically.28 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (7). Show columns only when there are unread items, mark read on mouse-over.29 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (6). Show only unique Tweets when copies appear in multiple columns.30 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (5). Show me more Tweets in each column via smaller text and magnify on mouse-over.32 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (4). Scheduler needs to allow me to tweet from any RSS feeds via my own web interface.36 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (3). Scheduler needs to allow me to schedule any number of Tweets for later delivery.36 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (2). FourSquare hack to allow me to become the mayor of any location automatically.42 minutes agoviaTweetDeck<BR/><BR/>Nice to have @TweetDeckhacks: (1). FourSquare hack to allow me to check-in to any locations at any time I wish automatically.            </en-note></en-note>]]></content><created>19700101T051353Z</created><updated>19700101T051353Z</updated><tag>TweetDeck</tag></note></en-export>
